==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: dà yú chī xiǎo yú, xiǎo yú chī xiāmǐ

===Etymology===
Literally: The big fish eat the little fish, and the little fish eat small shrimps.

===Proverb===
'''[[大魚吃小魚]]，[[小]][[魚]][[吃]][[蝦米]]'''


# The weak are the prey of the strong.

#: '''''大魚吃小魚，小魚吃蝦米'''，[[是]][[米]][[吃]][[爛泥]].''

===Alternate forms===
[[大鱼吃小鱼，小鱼吃虾米]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

